lead_paragraph: Mirim Lee shot a 10-under 62 on Thursday to match the Women's British Open record and open a three-stroke lead in the major championship at tree-lined Woburn Golf Club.

headline.print_headline: Mirim Lee Shoots 10-Under 62 to Tie Women's British Open
